WEBVTT

00:02:28.771 --> 00:02:30.724
on effectiveness and growth,

00:02:30.748 --> 00:02:32.918
taking better decisions --

00:02:32.942 --> 00:02:36.480
not replacing humans with AI
to save costs.

00:02:38.159 --> 00:02:41.359
Why is it important
to keep humans in the loop?

00:02:42.032 --> 00:02:46.879
Simply because, left alone,
AI can do very dumb things.

00:02:47.363 --> 00:02:50.736
Sometimes with no consequences,
like in this tweet.

00:02:51.212 --> 00:02:52.776
"Dear Amazon,

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:54.186
I bought a toilet seat.

00:02:54.210 --> 00:02:55.871
Necessity, not desire.

00:02:55.895 --> 00:02:57.347
I do not collect them,

00:02:57.371 --> 00:02:59.609
I'm not a toilet-seat addict.

00:02:59.633 --> 00:03:01.839
No matter how temptingly you email me,